{
  "stem": "8359.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother, I think, said to my father-- because I told you he came from a village that was a little further from where we lived, deeper into Poland.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father said, I'm not going anywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If I'm going to die, I want to die in my own house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was Friday morning that they invaded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Saturday, Sunday night, because we were already hearing on the radio that they're nearing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were not far from us at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We spent the whole night in an attic, the whole family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we heard them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't see them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we heard them, because of the tanks, the trucks, and the shootings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They just-- the Nazis--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family and some other neighbors, because we lived in an apartment building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And shooting-- we couldn't see anything, but we heard it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It seems we found out that they just-- coming into the city, they just shot whoever they saw in the streets.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't ask questions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were shooting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, we eventually had to come down from the attic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We couldn't stay there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, they just went on a rampage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They lined up the Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they went one, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, 10, boom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Just like this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shot.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They shot them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's also a very good question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Polish people, some of them helped them out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Listen, for them to-- in those days, to pull a man's pants down, and they knew right then and there that they're dealing with Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a very common thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I can't-- I mean, I don't remember exactly everything that happened after that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they set up a government provisional, whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, curfew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all we have had a curfew.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
